name: Stellar Transmuter Research Index File
description: This Stellar Transmuter Research Index File can be used as an input with a Stellar Transmuter Datacore Blueprint in order to reconstruct a portion of the accumulated research and technical data gathered by those empires with a comprehensive understanding of the means to construct and control Stellar Transmuters. To reconstruct such data it will also be necessary to acquire Stellar Transmuter Research Data Fragments and Encryption Keys.
